* Gander, Terry and Chamberlain, Peter. &quot;Weapons of the Third Reich: An Encyclopedic Survey of All Small Arms, Artillery and Special Weapons of the German Land Forces 1939-1945&quot;. New York: Doubleday, 1979 </text><links>
