=== Ricardo Rodríguez in the 24 Hours of Le Mans ===
*On 1958 24 Hours of Le Mans judged to be too young, 16-year-old Ricardo Rodríguez was not allowed to start by the organisers, Automobile Club de l&#x27;Ouest, so was replaced by José Behra, brother of Jean, to accompany his older brother, Pedro Rodríguez.

