*1974: Anthony Powell, &quot;Temporary Kings&quot;
*1975: Jon Stallworthy, &quot;Wilfred Owen&quot;
*1976: Seamus Heaney, &quot;North&quot;
*1977: Ronald Lewin, &quot;&quot;
